        "Details": "Developed as a super-fast scouting design, the Nyx Prototype is still being put through its paces by the Word of Blake. Designed for high speed and low drag, the Nyx is incredibly fast, able to keep pace with all but the absolute fastest units on the battlefield. Using Endo-Steel, Heavy Ferro-Fibrous, and a 300-rated XL fusion engine for weight savings, the Nyx still carries a respectable punch for its size. The NX-65 carries twin ER Medium Lasers as well as a MML-5. C3i ensures it can link easily with allied units during combat.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
